headline: Earnings Season Highlights on Tariffs, Consumer Spending, and More
summary: Back-to-school spending is strong, and other revelations from RBC’s reading of S&P 500 earnings-call transcripts. Plus, investment newsletter commentary on interest rates, agriculture, and healthcare stocks.

headline: William Blair Maintains Hold on NetApp (NTAP) Amid Product Margin Pressures
summary: NetApp Inc. (NASDAQ:NTAP) is one of the most undervalued and overlooked large-cap stocks. On August 27, William Blair’s Jason Ader maintained a Hold rating on NetApp Inc. (NASDAQ:NTAP) without assigning a price target. His neutral stance reflects the company’s mixed Q1 FY 2026 (FY ends in April) performance and its decision to reaffirm full-year guidance. In […]
